		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message27474117">Thinking about it, there really is not much competition in this category, it would have to go to Uchouten Kazoku. Other shows are simply more concerned with character driven stories. <br />
Though, I would be quick to agree that there are some problems with Uchouten's plot. Especially near the end. <br />
<br />
Novel adaptations will be hard to beat in this department.</div><div class="postActions"></div></td>
